# ── Environment / Secrets — NEVER commit these ────────────────────────────────
# SECURITY: .env contains publishable keys and project IDs.
# Even "safe" VITE_ vars leak your project ID and can be used for enumeration.
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.production
.env.staging
# Supabase service-role key (NEVER in frontend, but guard anyway)
.env.service

